Package com.github.shiftac.upartier.data

Class BString

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.shiftac.upartier.data.BString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ByteArrayIO

    public class BString
extends java.lang.Object
implements ByteArrayIO
    A multithread-safe String handler that implements ByteArrayIO and supports efficient calls of getBytes(). When transferring as bytes: 
     class BString
 {
    dword mlen;
    byte[mlen] mybytes;
 }
